Create Sample

To create a Sample:

  1. Click the Create/Upload button
  2.  Select the context you want the sample to be created

Note: Every object exists in the context of other objects. If there is no other object related to the current, it exists at least in the context of the user who created it. You can create the sample in the context of a cultural object or in the context of document, project or any folder. Creating sample in the context of another system objects means that this sample will be part of that context.

 

          3. ​Select "Sample" from the drop-down with types.

Note: To find easily the Sample in the list with system objects that can be created you can start to type directly in the field. The list with types is filtered as you write in the field.

 

​​​​         4. Fill mandatory sample data                        

​​​​         5. Press Create button
